rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0001
rows.name:
We should be reaching the uncharted
zone tomorrow, but there's plenty of
time left until then.

rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0002
rows.name:
I guess I could go and talk with
the clients for a bit?

rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0003
rows.name:
I still don't know as much about
them as I'd like to.

rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0004
rows.name:
Besides, it's not every day you get
to talk to real Drivers!

rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0005
rows.name:
Oh, and once I'm done with them,
I'd better go see Monell.

rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm meant to be on lookout duty
tonight - he won't be very pleased
if I never show up.
